</div>
<div class="news">
	<h3><a href="/zpravicky/prezentace-z-xtech-2006/">Prezentace z XTech 2006</a></h3>

	<div>Na <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/" hreflang="en" title="Main Page - MDC">Mozilla Developer Center</a> si můžete <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/XTech_2006_Presentations" hreflang="en" title="XTech 2006 Presentations - MDC">prohlédnout prezentace týkající se Mozilly</a>, přednesené na konferenci <a href="http://xtech06.usefulinc.com/" hreflang="en" title="XTech 2006: Building Web 2.0">XTech 2006</a> konané minulý týden v Amsterdamu. Záběr témat je široký: <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/presentations/xtech2006/javascript/" hreflang="en" title="JavaScript 2 and the Future of the Web">JavaScript 2</a>, <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/presentations/xtech2006/layout/slides/slide-1.xhtml" hreflang="en" title="Layout algorithm improvements for Web user interfaces">layout pro webová uživatelská rozhraní</a>, <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/presentations/xtech2006/microsummaries/" hreflang="en" title="Microsummaries in Firefox and on the Web">Microsummaries</a>, <a href="http://people.mozilla.com/~vladimir/xtech2006/" hreflang="en" title="SVG &amp; Canvas: Graphics for the Web">SVG + <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href="http://developer.mozilla.org/presentations/xtech2006/xulrunner/" hreflang="en" title="Converging Rich-Client and Web Application Development with Mozilla XULRunner (Open Office format)">XULRunner</a> a <a href="http://glazman.org/etna-xtech2006/" hreflang="en" title="Etna, a WYSIWYG XML RELAX NG- and Gecko-based editor"><abbr lang="en" title="Editing Tool for Networked Authors">Etna</abbr></a>.</div>
